594
00:30:31.874 --> 00:30:33.417
We. we. we raised him together.

595
00:30:33.417 --> 00:30:35.752
You can't just move
to another town
and shut me out.

596
00:30:35.752 --> 00:30:37.838
ANNE: Stop it. it's way overdue
we all moved on.

597
00:30:37.838 --> 00:30:41.049
