620
00:31:41.443 --> 00:31:43.111
(phone ringing)

621
00:31:44.112 --> 00:31:46.114
(beep)
BITTNER:Miss Calder?
Charles Bittner.

622
00:31:46.114 --> 00:31:47.157
Good news.

623
00:31:47.157 --> 00:31:49.243
We'd like you and your
family to come back

624
00:31:49.243 --> 00:31:51.161
