666
00:34:06.755 --> 00:34:10.092
probably not as entertaining as
Two Dinosaurs Meet
While Ice Skating.

667
00:34:10.717 --> 00:34:11.969
But it is just magical.
wouldn't you agree?

668
00:34:11.969 --> 00:34:13.512
Excuse me. Sir.

669
00:34:13.512 --> 00:34:14.888
