712
00:36:26.395 --> 00:36:27.938
(laughs)

713
00:36:40.158 --> 00:36:41.285
Please.

714
00:36:42.703 --> 00:36:44.580
And who are you?

715
00:36:45.330 --> 00:36:46.957
My thought exactly.

716
00:36:47.916 --> 00:36:49.376
(laughs)

717
00:36:49.376 --> 00:36:51.295
(jazz music crescendo)

718
00:36:52.379 --> 00:36:54.464
BITTNER: Go home.
