719
00:36:54.464 --> 00:36:56.341
ANNE: Why would you
invite us here
and then tell us to go home?

720
00:36:56.341 --> 00:36:57.926
Isn't the book from
your son's perspective?

721
00:36:57.926 --> 00:36:59.178
Er. yeah. but...

722
00:36:59.303 --> 00:37:00.929
BITTNER: Well. so he
should be here.

723
00:37:01.096 --> 00:37:03.223
